      "content": "oh okay good to know. i was getting a bit stressed about it. i read somewhere online that you have to watch out for toxic levels, but since you say it's just the adjustment period, i'll probably just drink a ton more water to be safe. i heard being hydrated helps keep the levels stable, right?",
